108
00:06:12,799 --> 00:06:15,880
That said, I do have a solution.

109
00:06:18,119 --> 00:06:19,799
Lord Liang, we can both put up a show.

110
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,679
Just let me whip you.

111
