214
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:11,319
if they have that
little bit of conscience,

215
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,280
they won't let mother

216
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,079
leave this world alone.

217
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:20,760
