of your days weeping.

235
00:18:36,359 --> 00:18:37,119
Qiu Min.

236
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:40,400
Qiu Min! Someone! Help!

237
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,160
Qiu Min!

238
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,920
