241
00:18:46,479 --> 00:18:47,479
Help!

242
00:18:47,719 --> 00:18:49,520
Qiu Min.

243
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:51,800
Qiu Min, are you okay?

244
00:18:51,959 --> 00:18:53,560
